quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  39,32,"Alaa Й“urЙ—o tooГұude haa hewta on dammbuЙ—o e Allah, ko yahdaani e Makko, wano waЙ—angol Mo kafidiiЙ—o, maa genndo maa Й“iЙ—Й—o. Alaa kadi Й“urЙ—o tooГұde wa on fennuЙ—o wahyu on mo NulaaЙ—o Allah on (yo o his) addi. E wonaa ka Yiite woni jaaЖҙorde yeddude Allah Й“en, Й“e yeddi ko NulaaЙ—o Makko on addi kon? Pellet, ko non woniri, weerde maЙ“Й“e, ko nder ton."
  39,33,"On non arduЙ—o e goonga, ka haala e ka kuuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, foti ko Annabaajo maa goЙ—Й—o goo, o gomЙ—ini Й—um, o gollitiri. Ko Й“en woni gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en tigiri, Й—oftiiЙ“e yamaruyeeji Joomi mun, woЙ—Й—itiiЙ“e haЙ—aaЙ—i Makko."
  39,34,"Hino woodani dakammeeji duumotooЙ—i, ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e; ko Й—um woni njoЙ“di moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e golle Й“en, ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e e jiyaaЙ“e."
  39,35,"Fii no Allah momtirana Й“e, ko Й“uri bonnde e ko Й“e gollaynoo e geddi aduna, tawde Й“e tuubii e mun, Й“e ruttike e Joomi maЙ“Й“e. O yoЙ“itira Й“e njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e ndin, ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e kon ko Й“e gollunoo."
  39,36,"Mbela Allah siforaali yonugol jeyaaЙ—o Makko on Muhammadu (yo o his) ka fiyakuuji makko diina e aduna, O duГұana mo ayЙ“e makko? Pellet, O yonay mo. HiЙ“e hulЙ“inire, an NulaaЙ—o, sabu majjere e Й—aayre maЙ“Й“e, Й—in sanamuuji, Й—i Й“e rewata Й“e acca Allah, wiide Й—i memirte bone. Kala non mo Allah hoyni, O hawrinaani mo fewnude, haray fewnoowo on Й—on, alaa."
  39,37,"Kala non mo Allah hawrindini e peewal, alaa haЙ—tanЙ—o majjinde mo. Mbela Allah siforaaki wonnde FooluЙ—o Mo gooto foolataa, Jom leptugol Й“en heefereЙ“e yedduЙ“e Mo? Ko non woniri, Ko O FooluЙ—o, Jom lepte."
  39,38,"Pellet, si an NulaaЙ—o, a lamndike Й“ee sirkooЙ“e: Ko hommbo tagi kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin? Ma Й“e wi'u: Ko Allah tagi Й—i. Awa maakan Й“e, feГұГұinanaaЙ“e, ronkere reweteeЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in: Yeetee lam fii Й—ii sanamuuji, Й—i rewoton gaanin Allah; si Allah faandanike lorra, hara Й—i waaway ittannde lam on lorra? Maa si O faandanike lam moЖҙЖҙere Makko, taw si Й—i haЙ—tani haЙ—ugol lam nden moЖҙЖҙere Makko? Maakan Й“ee: Allah tun yonii lam, ko e Makko mi fawi kala fiyaaku am, ko e Makko kadi tun, woni ko wakkiltoo Й“en tuuginotoo."
  39,39,"An NulaaЙ—o, maaku: Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, golliree no waalorani on, sirkangol Allah. Min ko no Joomi am yamirimmi non, mi gollirta, woni noddugol e tawhiidi, laЙ“Й“inana Mo dewal. Aray ka anndon, battane laawol kala e me'en."
  39,40,"Aray nde anndon, ko hommbo lepte aduna hoynayЙ—e aroyta e muuЙ—um, lepte duumiiЙ—e jippoyoo e makko Г‘alnde Darngal, hara Й—e taЖҙondirtaa, sakko Й—e lanna."